## Performance Requirements
- Lighthouse score target: 95+ on Performance, 100 on SEO, 100 on Accessibility, 100 on Best Practices
- All images: WebP format, with `width` and `height` attributes set, `loading="lazy"` on non-hero images
- Hero image or background: `loading="eager"`, `fetchpriority="high"`
- No unused CSS (Tailwind purges automatically)
- No render-blocking scripts
- Google Fonts loaded with `rel="preconnect"` and `display=swap`
